WELCOME_HELP_DESCRIPTION: Change settings for when users joins the server.
WELCOME_HELP_USAGE: Set a role for users to gain upon joinging the server.```/welcome role <role>```
Disable settings for users to gain a role upon joining.```/welcome disable```
WELCOME_ENABLE: Users will now get the role %s upon joining the server.
WELCOME_DISABLE: Users will no longer get a role upon joining the server.
